  "description": "A hummingbird is delicately extracting nectar from a vibrant, flowering plant. The plant features numerous tubular, reddish-brown blossoms clustered around a central stalk. The hummingbird's long, slender beak is inserted into one of the flowers, and its iridescent feathers are partially visible. The background is a soft, blurred wash of green and blue, suggesting foliage and sky, creating a shallow depth of field that emphasizes the bird and flowers. Sunlight illuminates the scene, creating highlights and shadows on the plant and hummingbird.",
